{"tid":680002,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴塞官方恭喜皇馬：祝賀皇馬奪得歐冠盃冠軍","createTime":"2018-05-27T01:52:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T05:06:29.000Z","uid":34571,"like":65,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ad861e5396d3cdd5ae3e692bc13f3f680ec641e8","tid":680002,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T01:52:04.000Z","msg":"皇馬又一次奪得了歐冠盃冠軍，而作為他們的死敵，巴塞也通過官方渠道對皇馬錶示了祝賀。<br />\n<br />\n　　今季巴塞在歐冠盃上的遭遇堪稱恥辱，在8強戰中他們面對羅馬，在第一回合4-1的巨大優勢下，第二回合卻在羅馬主場被對手3-0逆轉反勝，落寞地與歐冠盃告別。好在他們之後順利奪得了西甲和西班牙盃的冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n　　<br />\n<br />\n　　而皇馬則一路過關斬將，先後淘汰了巴黎、祖記、拜仁，並在決賽中擊敗利物浦捧得了他們歷史上第13座歐冠盃獎盃。雖然皇馬的歐冠盃戰績令人羨慕，但巴塞在賽後還是大方地為皇馬送上了祝賀，他們的官方Twitter寫道：「恭喜皇馬奪得了2017-18賽季歐冠盃的冠軍。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2018/05/27/6/6443a08f4c6b2e4585f934e58ba32c6b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F6%2F6443a08f4c6b2e4585f934e58ba32c6b.jpg&h=0bfbd35f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec57a03ff0f904302c2a9a0473deb0d704529b69","tid":680002,"uid":53736,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T01:57:44.000Z","msg":"賤種蝗會話好撚虛偽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"459dffbd4fdba3b76e80079182f5acf771ae4f81","tid":680002,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T01:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a22c6e7cdf0f38e853aff427c38d16c58c10a287","tid":680002,"uid":38172,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T02:05:15.000Z","msg":"有風度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd3a2c7a9ae4898a92567369ba231a45e2363d94","tid":680002,"uid":186,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy